Cutthroat knocked Sinnertwin totally over, as he landed in a pile on the
ground. One of his head was untangeld, "Cutthroat always hit from behind,
grrrrrrr, you not better" but he couldnt get up.

The small odd looking creature talking to Hung-grr turned towards them, and
whirled changing to another head to look at the barberic behaviour. They
were wasteful, and dificult to control, why did his superiors insist they
be brought. "Blot, Cutthroat, Sinnertwin, stop that wasteful display at
once". He looked visibly upset.
